Name: AccountCurrencyCode
Notes: The currency of the Customer account.

Name: AccountDescriptiveName
Notes: The descriptive name of the Customer account.

Name: AccountTimeZoneId
Notes: Name of the timezone selected for the Customer account. For example: "(GMT-05:00) Eastern Time". This field does not reflect the current state of daylight saving time for the timezone.

Name: AdGroupId
Notes: The ID of the AdGroup.

Name: AdGroupName
Notes: The name of the AdGroup.

Name: AdGroupStatus
Enum Values:
UNKNOWN / unknown
ENABLED / enabled
PAUSED / paused
REMOVED / removed
Notes: Status of the ad group.

Name: AverageCpc
Notes: The total cost of all clicks divided by the total number of clicks received.

Name: AverageCpm
Notes: Average Cost-per-thousand impressions (CPM).

Name: CampaignId
Notes: The ID of the Campaign.

Name: CampaignName
Notes: The name of the Campaign.

Name: CampaignStatus
Enum Values:
UNKNOWN / unknown
ENABLED / enabled
PAUSED / paused
REMOVED / removed
Notes: The status of the Campaign.

Name: Category0
Notes: Top level theme category of the pages in your website domain.

Name: Category1
Notes: First level theme category of the pages in your website domain.

Name: Category2
Notes: Second level theme category of the pages in your website domain.

Name: ClickConversionRate
Notes: The number of converted clicks divided by your total clicks that can be tracked to a conversion. This is how often a click on your ad resulted in a conversion. Percentage returned as "x.xx%".

Name: Clicks
Notes: The number of clicks.

Name: ConversionRateManyPerClick
Notes: The number of conversions divided by total clicks that can be tracked to conversions. Percentage returned as "x.xx%".

Name: ConversionsManyPerClick
Notes: This column reports total conversions, across all the conversion actions you're tracking. How you've chosen to count your conversions (unique or all) affects the number shown in this column.

Name: ConvertedClicks
Notes: The number of clicks that converted within your chosen conversion window.

Name: Cost
Notes: The sum of your cost-per-click (CPC) and cost-per-thousand impressions (CPM) costs during this period. Other costs such as cost-per-call aren't included. For a sum of all costs, use the TotalCost column.

Name: CostPerConversionManyPerClick
Notes: Total cost divided by your total conversions.

Name: CostPerConvertedClick
Notes: Cost divided by your total converted clicks.

Name: CriterionId
Notes: The Criterion ID.

Name: Ctr
Notes: The number of clicks your ad receives (Clicks) divided by the number of times your ad is shown (Impressions). Percentage returned as "x.xx%".

Name: CustomerDescriptiveName
Notes: The descriptive name of the Customer.

Name: Date
Notes: The date formatted as yyyy-MM-dd.

Name: DayOfWeek
Enum Values:
MONDAY / Monday
TUESDAY / Tuesday
WEDNESDAY / Wednesday
THURSDAY / Thursday
FRIDAY / Friday
SATURDAY / Saturday
SUNDAY / Sunday
Notes: The name of the day of the week, e.g., "Monday".

Name: Domain
Notes: On the Keywordless Query and Category reports, the domain of the dynamically selected destination URL of the impression. On the other reports, the domain of the URL (placement) where the impression was shown.

Name: ExternalCustomerId
Notes: The Customer ID.

Name: Impressions
Notes: Count of how often your ad has appeared on a search results page or website on the Google Network.

Name: Month
Notes: The first day of the month, formatted as yyyy-MM-dd.

Name: MonthOfYear
Enum Values:
JANUARY / January
FEBRUARY / February
MARCH / March
APRIL / April
MAY / May
JUNE / June
JULY / July
AUGUST / August
SEPTEMBER / September
OCTOBER / October
NOVEMBER / November
DECEMBER / December
Notes: The name of the month of the year, e.g., "December".

Name: PrimaryCompanyName
Notes: Company name of the account.

Name: Quarter
Notes: The first day of the quarter, formatted as yyyy-MM-dd. Uses the calendar year for quarters, e.g., the second quarter of 2014 starts on 2014-04-01.

Name: ValuePerConversionManyPerClick
Notes: The total value of all conversions divided by the total number of conversions.

Name: ValuePerConvertedClick
Notes: The total value of all conversions divided by the total number of converted clicks.

Name: Week
Notes: The date for the Monday of the week, formatted as yyyy-MM-dd.

Name: Year
Notes: The year, formatted as yyyy.
